            </ul>

            <h3>Files Removed</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>🗑️ <code>Comserv/root/navigation/</code> - Entire duplicate directory removed</li>
                <li>🗑️ <code>Comserv/root/Navigation/navigation_backup.tt</code> - Temporary backup file removed</li>
            </ul>
